    },
    {
      "start": 720.04,
      "end": 725.64,
      "text": "제가 I just moved in, 막 이사 왔고 and but thanks, 고마워요."
    },
    {
      "start": 725.74,
      "end": 727.14,
      "text": "I really appreciate it."
    },
    {
      "start": 727.4,
      "end": 728.54,
      "text": "정말 고마워요."
    },
    {
      "start": 728.84,
      "end": 729.92,
      "text": "거주하기 좋은 방법이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 730.04,
      "end": 730.42,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 730.5,
      "end": 732.84,
      "text": "I would love to, you know, but thanks."
    },
    {
      "start": 732.84,
      "end": 734.72,
      "text": "You know, I can't."
    },
    {
      "start": 734.72,
      "end": 738.28,
      "text": "예, but 뒤에 연결이 되는 부분이 진짜 핵심적인 내용이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 739.18,
      "end": 740.82,
      "text": "The invitation is sweet."
    },
    {
      "start": 741.06,
      "end": 743.86,
      "text": "음, 그러면서 the invitation is sweet."
    },
    {
      "start": 744.24,
      "end": 746.48,
      "text": "아, 초대도 해주고 너무 고맙네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 746.68,
      "end": 750.74,
      "text": "라고 마무리를 어떻게든 해보려고 노력을 하는 말사였습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 751.2,
      "end": 751.94,
      "text": "아, 곤란해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 752.12,
      "end": 753.52,
      "text": "예, 아, 첫날인데."
    },
    {
      "start": 754.06,
      "end": 759.78,
      "text": "아무튼 they have 진짜로 opposite personalities를 가지고 있는 게 되게 흥미로웠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 759.94,
      "end": 761.12,
      "text": "Like fire and water."
    },
    {
      "start": 761.22,
      "end": 761.5,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 761.58,
      "end": 762.38,
      "text": "Oil and water."
    },
    {
      "start": 762.38,
      "end": 764.22,
      "text": "물과 기름일까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 764.38,
      "end": 765.4,
      "text": "물과 불일까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 765.66,
      "end": 767.1,
      "text": "앞으로 잘 봐봐야 되겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 767.32,
      "end": 769.38,
      "text": "They can hit it off really, really fast."
    },
    {
      "start": 769.5,
      "end": 771.48,
      "text": "Or they can crash and burn."
    },
    {
      "start": 771.62,
      "end": 772.92,
      "text": "둘 중에 하나이겠네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 773.12,
      "end": 774.88,
      "text": "Let's see how it goes."
    },
    {
      "start": 775.72,
      "end": 777.1,
      "text": "네, 한 번 더 확인해 보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 777.82,
      "end": 779.7,
      "text": "Hey, you don't play poker, do you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 779.76,
      "end": 781.92,
      "text": "Because I run a weekly game."
    },
    {
      "start": 782.04,
      "end": 784.72,
      "text": "And we could sure use another player."
    },
    {
      "start": 784.72,
      "end": 786.22,
      "text": "It's all very hush-hush."
    },
    {
      "start": 786.4,
      "end": 788.94,
      "text": "Because gambling's not allowed around here."
    },
    {
      "start": 789.04,
      "end": 790.46,
      "text": "Like most things that are worthwhile."
    },
    {
      "start": 790.46,
      "end": 793.82,
      "text": "You should drop by tonight and say hi to the guy."
    },
    {
      "start": 793.92,
      "end": 797.18,
      "text": "God, you know, it's been a very, look, it's a long day for me."
    },
    {
      "start": 797.24,
      "end": 798.06,
      "text": "I just moved in."
    },
    {
      "start": 798.26,
      "end": 798.72,
      "text": "But thanks."
    },
    {
      "start": 798.8,
      "end": 801.4,
      "text": "I really appreciate what you're at the invitation suite."
    },
    {
      "start": 801.4,
      "end": 803.99,
      "text": "잘 들어보셨죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 804.59,
      "end": 805.53,
      "text": "유지영님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 805.53,
      "end": 807.63,
      "text": "크쌤 한국말 실력처럼"
    },
    {
      "start": 807.63,
      "end": 811.31,
      "text": "제 영어 실력도 일치월장 했으면 좋겠어요 하셨습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 811.55,
      "end": 812.19,
      "text": "가능합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 813.65,
      "end": 815.53,
      "text": "가능하다고 이야기해 주셨으니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 815.65,
      "end": 816.27,
      "text": "일치월장."
    },
    {
      "start": 816.51,
      "end": 817.41,
      "text": "You can do it."
    },
    {
      "start": 817.49,
      "end": 818.21,
      "text": "하실 수 있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 818.29,
      "end": 818.69,
      "text": "Come on."
    },
    {
      "start": 819.59,
      "end": 822.23,
      "text": "에너지를 뿜뿜 받아가시면 좋겠고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 822.69,
      "end": 825.57,
      "text": "Oh, and anyway, what are you doing for tomorrow?"
    },
    {
      "start": 825.95,
      "end": 826.65,
      "text": "What am I doing tomorrow?"
    },
    {
      "start": 826.77,
      "end": 828.19,
      "text": "What day is it tomorrow?"
    },
    {
      "start": 828.19,
      "end": 829.47,
      "text": "어린이날."
    },
    {
      "start": 829.65,
      "end": 830.73,
      "text": "아, Children's Day."
    },
    {
      "start": 830.81,
      "end": 833.19,
      "text": "아, 이거 계획 있으셔야 하는 거 아닙니까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 833.27,
      "end": 834.35,
      "text": "아, 계획 미리 짰습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 834.53,
      "end": 835.63,
      "text": "For your lovely two daughters."
    },
    {
      "start": 835.95,
      "end": 837.37,
      "text": "I made a plan."
    },
    {
      "start": 837.55,
      "end": 840.95,
      "text": "The plan is to, I got a video game for them."
    },
    {
      "start": 841.11,
      "end": 841.47,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 841.55,
      "end": 842.81,
      "text": "And we live on the first floor."
    },
    {
      "start": 842.97,
      "end": 845.77,
      "text": "And it's a game the family can all play together."
    },
    {
      "start": 845.89,
      "end": 847.13,
      "text": "Because we don't have a TV."
    },
    {
      "start": 847.43,
      "end": 849.09,
      "text": "We're going to put it on the projector."
    },
    {
      "start": 849.33,
      "end": 849.57,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 849.65,
      "end": 850.95,
      "text": "And dance together."
    },
    {
      "start": 851.07,
      "end": 851.99,
      "text": "It's a dancing game."
    },
    {
      "start": 851.99,
      "end": 852.59,
      "text": "Good idea."
    },
    {
      "start": 853.55,
      "end": 854.15,
      "text": "좋아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 854.33,
      "end": 855.79,
      "text": "아이들도 너무 좋아할 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 856.11,
      "end": 856.77,
      "text": "I hope they like it."
    },
    {
      "start": 857.51,
      "end": 858.75,
      "text": "네, 잘 보내시고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 858.89,
      "end": 861.23,
      "text": "우리는 다음 주에 건강하게 다시 뵐게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 861.55,
      "end": 861.93,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 862.09,
      "end": 862.85,
      "text": "Happy Children's Day."
    },
    {
      "start": 862.95,
      "end": 863.45,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 863.47,
      "end": 863.65,
      "text": "Bye."
    }
  ]
}